OL,5,Crights'
OL,7,FA review into the care given by one of
OL,8,Fthe country's largest mental health
OL,9,Fproviders in the country has found
OL,10,Fthat staff were unkind and abusive
OL,11,Ftowards patients, and that leaders
OL,12,Fcontributed to "a culture of fear and
OL,13,Fintimidation".
OL,15,FThe review into the Mental Health
OL,16,FTrust (GMMH) was commissioned by NHS
OL,17,FEngland in November 2022 after a host
OL,18,Fof failings to vulnerable patients
OL,19,Fcame to light at the in .
