OL,4,Cpatients were denied 'basic human
OL,5,Crights'
OL,7,FThe report's final findings were
OL,8,Fpublished on 31 January 2024, and
OL,9,Ffound that patient care across the
OL,10,Ftrust has "at times been poor" and
OL,11,Fthat patients have been "denied basic
OL,12,Fdignity and their human rights".
OL,14,FIt found that there were repeated
OL,15,Fmissed opportunities to act on the
OL,16,Fconcerns raised at the Edenfield
OL,17,FCentre by patients and their families.
