OL,7,FThe report said: "A large part of what
OL,8,Fwas exposed... was due to the lack of
OL,9,Fvalue placed on the patient's voice in
OL,10,FGMMH, as well as a frequent disregard
OL,11,Ffor the experiences of families and
OL,12,Fcarers.
OL,14,F"It is clear that patients and their
OL,15,Floved ones had raised, on various
OL,16,Foccasions, serious concerns about the
OL,17,Fcare provided at Edenfield and
OL,18,Felsewhere in the Trust, and that this
OL,19,Fhad not aways been taken seriously."
