OL,7,F"Several leaders (were) identified by
OL,8,Fstaff as displaying these behaviours
OL,9,Fremain in senior and influential
OL,10,Fposts; our review found that some of
OL,11,Fthese individuals do not appear to
OL,12,Funderstand how their behaviours might
OL,13,Fhave contributed to the problems at
OL,14,FGMMH."
OL,16,FThe lengthy new report details the
OL,17,Freasons why the abuse at Edenfield
OL,18,FCentre was allowed to proliferate, as
OL,19,Fwell as the wider problems causing
OL,20,Fhavoc across the trust.
