OL,7,FIt said: "We found a service that had
OL,8,Fall the hallmarks of a closed culture,
OL,9,Fincluding an absence of psychological
OL,10,Fsafety, incivility between staff, poor
OL,11,Fleadership, and a lack of teamworking."
OL,13,FThe report was critical of the trust's
OL,14,Fleadership, with some 'senior and
OL,15,Finfluential' leaders still in post
OL,16,Fdespite contributing to a culture of
OL,17,F'fear and intimidation'.
