OL,7,FThe report said: "At Edenfield it was
OL,8,Fnot uncommon for a single qualified
OL,9,Fnurse to have to assume responsibility
OL,10,Ffor three wards.
OL,12,F"We heard of newly qualified nurses
OL,13,Ftaking on leadership roles that they
OL,14,Fwere ill equipped to deal with, often
OL,15,Fwith little practical support or
OL,16,Fsupervision.
