OL,7,F"We heard of high levels of turnover
OL,8,Facross all disciplines, but especially
OL,9,Famong consultant psychiatrists. These
OL,10,Fworkforce pressures likely had a
OL,11,Fsignificant impact on the safety,
OL,12,Fexperience and effectiveness of the
OL,13,Fcare provided."
OL,15,FAfter reports in the media, the trust
OL,16,Fwas ordered to improve by health
OL,17,Fwatchdogs the Care Quality Commission
OL,18,F(CQC), and thrust into police and
OL,19,Findependent investigations.
